{
  "stem": "11744.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I was-- I was completely alone with the kids.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's when I put the kids in the Chambon again, and I started with the children homes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I start-- we started to build children homes after children homes to all the kids that we had kept in hiding.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we tried to get them all in Jewish homes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "To--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, immediately, I had to do something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I was responsible for my children, and I was alone, and I, immediately, had to do something.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then I was going to work, and then finally, someone said, look, there is absolutely no way out for you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can't, you can't because the kids have to be taken back and they have to be put together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We finally ended up with 1,100 children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We made-- we had 15 homes, and we had 1,100 children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of them were hidden, and a lot of them came back-- some came back from Buchenwald, some came back from other camps.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "None of them came back from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Bigger ones did-- older ones did come from Auschwitz, because I had two sisters-- and one was in the east part of Auschwitz, the other one in the west.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They never knew they were in camp together, and they found themselves in my home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They suddenly discovered that the two of them were alive, and they had both been in Auschwitz, and didn't know anything about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were liberated on August 24-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and he was still in German-- in German territory, so it must have been-- wait.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [NON-ENGLISH] It must have been about-- about three, four weeks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that-- that we fought-- for that we fought very hard.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
